## Kevin Trethewey

Kevin has a strong technical background after more than a decade in the software industry as a developer and architect.

Over the course of his career he has had the opportunity to work in and observe projects and teams in vastly different environments, and seen vastly differing levels of success amongst them.

###Specialties
Through experience Kevin has developed an eye for what works and what doesn't, and a drive for assisting and empowering companies (and people!) to embrace and adapt to an Agile way of life

